Comando nrpe /Command nrpe

command[unidades_montadas]=/usr/local/nagios/libexec/check_mountpoints -A

*IMPORTANTE: verificar la ruta de los plugins, ya que en ocasiones en lugar de libexec aparece plugins.
*IMPORTANT: validate the path of plugins, ocasinally appear libexex, in another case appear plugins.

Comando/Command

define command {
       command_name                             check_nrpe_mountpoints
       command_line                             $USER1$/check_nrpe -H $HOSTADDRESS$ -c check_mountpoints
}

Servicio/Service

define service {
        host_name                       HOSTNAME
        service_description             Unidades Montadas
        use                             generic-service
        check_command                   check_nrpe!unidades_montadas
        max_check_attempts              1
        check_interval                  1
        retry_interval                  1
        check_period                    xi_timeperiod_24x7
        notification_interval           60
        notification_period             xi_timeperiod_24x7
        contacts                        CONTACTOS
        register                        1
        }

comando para probar desde el server
Command for test from server

/usr/local/nagios/libexec/check_nrpe -H IP-HOSTNAME -c unidades_montadas

Comando para probar localmente
Command for test local

sh /usr/local/nagios/libexec/check_mountpoints -A
